    "updated_at": "2016-01-10T22:06:22Z",
    "body": "Here is one more screenshot. In this screenshot the window should be positioned in the bottom left of the screen - you can see there is padding on the left, bottom, and right. Interestingly, the `y` value seems to be working correctly, so if you set `y` to zero it will appropriately put the window right at the top of the screen.\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/62191/12224363/4619767e-b7a3-11e5-975b-b882838ca66f.png)\n"
