    "updated_at": "2016-01-11T07:34:13Z",
    "body": "Windows 10 has a thinner frame than before, and in order to be compatible with existing apps it is returning wrong values in its win32 APIs. You can reproduce the same problem in Chrome browser:\n\n<img width=\"1058\" alt=\"screen shot 2016-01-11 at 3 25 55 pm\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/639601/12228532/d726e7b2-b877-11e5-9c2a-59f466da93ca.png\">\n\nI have reported the problem to upstream: https://crbug.com/576192.\n"
  },
